bcmApp/ui
This directory houses PyDM UI software.


bcm_summary.py
    The default screen. Shows a summary of the most important information for the instrument and provides
    a link to the expert screen

bcm_expert.ui
bcm_expert.py
    The expert screen. Shows all the summary information as well as the BPM link status and gives links to
    other specific expert screens.

fpga_config.ui
fpga_config.py
    The Expert Expert screen.
    Screen for uploading/saving YAML config files, launching the TreeGUI for direct register access,
    and displaying FW build information.
